{"tid":1962770,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[4月新番] 邪神與廚二病少女 / 小邪神飛踢 / 邪神ちゃんドロップキック","createTime":"2020-04-07T16:37:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-08T04:03:57.000Z","uid":189068,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"c08e887762ade93748f98cb696bd25fc6250620c","tid":1962770,"uid":189068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T16:37:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.acgsecrets.hk/img/57/578306329ce484feaba20c37d65196c5/aaa22dcd7a66a836ff449b6550ff484f1d6360784d5114e86d4ff9e0870069b2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.acgsecrets.hk%2Fimg%2F57%2F578306329ce484feaba20c37d65196c5%2Faaa22dcd7a66a836ff449b6550ff484f1d6360784d5114e86d4ff9e0870069b2.jpg&h=8df9368c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n故事講述一位中二病女大學生花園百合鈴偶然從魔界召喚了惡魔小邪神，卻不知道讓小邪神回去的方法。小邪神說讓召喚者死亡就行了，於是小邪神為了回到魔界開始各種暗殺行動，然而花園百合鈴擁有徹底碾壓小邪神的強大武力，因此兩人被迫展開日常喜劇的同居生活。 <br />\n<br />\n<ins>簡介Source from Wiki</ins><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n動畫官網<br />\n<a href=\"http://jashinchan.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fjashinchan.com%2F&d=BHyrWEjohbhGCquuSPOYYpB82cw%2Bhl0zMn8EQHxvzrU%3D&h=1361dcbe\" target=\"_blank\">http://jashinchan.com/</a><br />\n<br />\nPV:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Gywp0Wobrnw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DGywp0Wobrnw&d=BHyrWEjohbhGCquuSPOYYpB82cw%2Bhl0zMn8EQHxvzrU%3D&h=1b7a6e8d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Gywp0Wobrnw</a><br />\n<br />\nOP:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kEQ3tEGKUa0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DkEQ3tEGKUa0&d=BHyrWEjohbhGCquuSPOYYpB82cw%2Bhl0zMn8EQHxvzrU%3D&h=86b3d0b7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kEQ3tEGKUa0</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n配音員<br />\n邪神ちゃん：鈴木愛奈<br />\n花園ゆりね：大森日雅<br />\nメデューサ：久保田未夢<br />\nぺこら：小坂井祐莉絵<br />\nミノス：小見川千明<br />\nぽぽろん：佐々木李子<br />\nペルセポネ2世：飯田里穂<br />\n橘芽依：原奈津子<br />\n遊佐：荒浪和沙<br />\n浩二：寺田御子<br />\nぴの：山田麻莉奈<br />\nキョンキョン：山下七海<br />\nキョンキョンの姉：田中美海<br />\nベート：M・A・O<br />\n悪魔A：遊佐浩二<br />\n<br />\n製作人員<br />\n原作：ユキヲ<br />\n製作總指揮：夏目公一朗<br />\n總導演：佐藤光<br />\n導演：矢野孝典<br />\n劇本統籌：筆安一幸<br />\n編劇：筆安一幸、村上桃子<br />\n人物設計：古賀誠<br />\n總作畫監督：古賀誠<br />\n色彩設計：野口幸恵<br />\n音樂：栗原悠希、神馬譲<br />\n音效指導：今泉雄一<br />\n音響制作：エスタ―セブン<br />\n動畫製作：ノーマッド"},{"pid":"6aebb999251acccbf0b48047a6eee6da14bac7eb","tid":1962770,"uid":51665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T16:40:23.000Z","msg":"第2季全套終於睇哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"550b03c08f8d54b52c0561df9e78f54b39e01b68","tid":1962770,"uid":34378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T16:41:55.000Z","msg":"標題冇寫第二季<br />\n心諗唔係已經動畫化過啦咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d67b8a43a8ec843f58b5779b7ea401aec22aa221","tid":1962770,"uid":189068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"550b03c08f8d54b52c0561df9e78f54b39e01b68","tid":1962770,"uid":34378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T16:41:55.000Z","msg":"標題冇寫第二季<br />\n心諗唔係已經動畫化過啦咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T16:47:15.000Z","msg":"漏左<br />\n重唔重開好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d90f6049c18f1481fb555031d364520fe717b473","tid":1962770,"uid":118709,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T17:01:36.000Z","msg":"岩岩山田麻莉奈親身cosplayぴの...超正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce00126402941ddec09294617b2d634ea13db05c","tid":1962770,"uid":331814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T17:04:06.000Z","msg":"正野"},{"pid":"87a763fc4c1b1461626583931d5261c88e835259","tid":1962770,"uid":197103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d90f6049c18f1481fb555031d364520fe717b